[There have been some sensationalist reports stating the passengers had free reign of the ship and were able to walk all around, a situation that is reminiscent of measles parties in the pre-vaccine era. The media report above paints an appropriate picture of a well thought out quarantine strategy with avoidance of potential disease transmission. - Mod.MPP]

